        "id": 5145
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-05-11T15:04:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It was a little strange to see childName used here and at the top-level.\nMight be more clearer by calling this childDisplayName (or something better), if not specified then it will use childName from top-level. Up to you if we also want a parentDisplayName with similar logic. I can see it being useful to also be able to specify that.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 6,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 6,
        "endChar": 14
      },
      "revId": "66a17d69912fbdff727c9d9ec1fb52b6ee7b433e",
