      "writtenOn": "2020-05-11T15:04:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We probably do not want this done everywhere and I would hope this is no longer needed for Android. Let\u0027s remove and see what happens?\n\nBut these kinds of hacks maybe shows the need to be able to do something like this in commit_msg/android.go ?\nIt could be that one day some roller needs a special commit msg hack that does not make sense in any other roller, how would we do that hack? add an if stmt here using c.ChildName or serverURL maybe",
      "revId": "66a17d69912fbdff727c9d9ec1fb52b6ee7b433e",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
